This is the Glulx component of Schmalz, the Erlang Interactive
Fiction system.

Description:
------------
Glulx is a virtual machine 

Status:
-------

Currently, Glulx support is in the prototyping and concept phase. It can
run a couple of thousand lines of "Adventure" and "Risorgimento Represso"
before crashing.
Also, this VM includes a rudimentary Glk implementation.



